    <string name="about_app" >About CashQuest</string>
    <string name="intro_about" >Embark on an adventure to conquer your finances with CashQuest, the game-like budgeting app that turns personal finance into an engaging journey.</string>
    <string name="about_middle">Set your sights on achieving financial goals while leveling up your skills, just like in a game. Whether you’re tracking expenses, managing income, or strategizing your next financial move, CashQuest makes every step of the journey fun and rewarding.</string>
    <string name="more_about">CashQuest is more than a budgeting app—it\'s your personal financial companion, equipped with tools to:</string>
    <string name="about_features">
    ‣ Set and Achieve Goals: Define your financial objectives and work towards them.\n
    ‣ Track Income and Expenses: Easily log and categorize your spending.\n
    ‣ Visualize Progress: View intuitive graphs that give you actionable insights into your spending habits.\n
    ‣ Earn Rewards: Stay motivated with badges, EXP points, and quests that make financial management a game you’ll want to win.</string>
    <string name="about_conclusion">Transform your financial future one level at a time—CashQuest makes it easy, fun, and effective. Join us today and start your quest toward financial mastery!"</string>

